➜父母在和幼儿说英语晚安，不一样的表达
http://www.sohu.com/a/374559703_100171577	31966
<p>晚安的英文学习,除了全世界都知道的"good night"，今天就来学习不一样的说“晚安”的表达。</p>
<p>Nighty Night / Sweet dreams! / Sleep well / Night Night.</p>
<p>Lights out! / Sleep tight! / Dream of me / Until tomorrow.</p>
<p>Always and forever! / Have a good sleep / Dream about me!</p>
<p>Go to bed, you sleepy head!</p>
<p>Time to ride the rainbow to dreamland!</p>
<p>Don’t forget to say your prayers!</p>
<p>Goodnight, the little love of my life!</p>
<p>I’ll be right here in the morning.</p>
<p>I’ll be dreaming of you!</p>
<p>Dream of Mama/Papa! </p>
<p>Sleep well, my little prince/princess!</p>
<p>Jesus loves you, and so do I!</p>
<p>Sleep snug as a bug in a rug!</p>
<p>I’ll be dreaming of your face!</p>
<p>I’m so lucky to have you, Sweetheart!</p>
<p>I love you to the stars and back!</p>
<p>I’ll dream of you tonight and see you tomorrow, my love.</p>
<p>I can’t imagine myself with anyone else!</p>
<p>If you need me, you know where to find me.</p>
<p>Goodnight, the love of my life!</p>
<p>Can’t wait to wake up next to you!</p>
<p>另外，父母在和孩子说晚安的时候，不妨再加上一句，妈妈爱你的话。让孩子被更多的爱所环绕。语言的力量是非常强大的，当我们给孩子更多正向的语言激励，可以帮助孩子成长的更加优秀。欢迎关注西苏英语官 网（http://www.ciseedu.cn/index.html），这里有更多的教育资讯，有奇趣的的活动，有趣的文章。</p>
